Name: Super Turbo Demon Busters!
About the game: UBER-FAST Rapid and unforgiving gameplay where you will run away from hazards and combat monsters. TURBO-RANDOM Every level is generated, every situation is unique. SUPER-DEEP A plenty of heroes to lead and tons of weapons to fire. So, your beloved superiors have just landed you, by mistake, on a home world of every monster, virus and hazard in our galaxy. Time is running out before you either burn or, worse, become one of them. Lead a squad of hardcore space marines and mercenaries through the hell made by the devoted fans of DOOM and ALIEN.
